        <abstract> 
<p>The work of the <hi rend="italic">Zoology</hi> is now completed. The Smith, Elder &amp; Co. account for the second number of part five is presented. CD expresses his "grateful thanks" to the Lords Commissioners.</p> 
        </abstract>
